item.description:
HOW TO: Give Yourself A Manicure
Follow me on twitter! http://www.twitter.com/juicystar007 So I hope you guys learn that you can get a full manicure without leaving the house or spending the money! It's also a fun way to relax and have a little bit of "you" time. I like to do this 2-4 times a week, and switch up the colors of polish! What you need: nail polish remover cotton balls bowl of warm water nail clippers nail file (glass one preferably) cuticle oil (i used seacret from the dead sea) cuticle pusher hand lotion/ cream (i used CND scentsations in mango and coconut) base coat (i used seche crystal clear base coat) nail polish in color of your choice (i used OPI "do you lilac it?") top coat (i used seche fast drying top coat) OPI drip dry (optional for faster drying)
